                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.911/7–1349: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cabot</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-07-13T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 13, 1949—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1401. Urtel 2740. Dept believes time opportune to give publicity Miner as well as
                    similar cases where violence condoned by authorities. Dept would prefer take
                    occasion lodging of joint consular protest for this action. If joint protest
                    unlikely or delayed please inform, in which case Dept will immediately proceed
                    publicity these cases.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
